{"tid":1964251,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"歐盟向支那不鏽鋼課反傾銷稅14.5%至18.9%","createTime":"2020-04-08T16:26:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-09T03:05:00.000Z","uid":75656,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8f5e2cf45a7a17098b2efc49db10bbc749251f8f","tid":1964251,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T16:26:35.000Z","msg":"〔財經頻道／綜合報導〕歐盟去年對台灣、中國和印尼的熱軋不鏽鋼板和捲材出口商啟動反傾銷調查，以查明3國的業者是否在歐洲，以低於成本的價格銷售產品，而據歐盟今（8）日消息，其將對進口自台灣、中國和印尼的熱軋不鏽鋼板和捲材，徵收臨時反傾銷關稅，關稅稅率從6％至18.9％，其中台灣稅率最高達7.5%。<br />\n<br />\n據歐盟今日消息和公報，歐盟執委會（European Commission）今天起對台灣、中國和印尼的不鏽鋼板和捲材，徵收稅率最高達18.9％的臨時反傾銷稅，實施有效期限最長為6個月，在此期間內，歐盟執委會將繼續進行調查，並決定是否採其他措施。<br />\n<br />\n而對台灣、中國和印尼的熱軋不鏽鋼板和捲材關稅稅率，則分別為6%或7.5%；14.5%或18.9%；17%，此外，歐盟執委會也正對同類商品進行反補貼調查。<br />\n<br />\n據公報內容，歐盟執委會在歐洲鋼鐵協會（The European Steel Association, EUROFER）於2019年6月28日，代表包括芬蘭的生產商Outokumpu、西班牙的Acerinox、荷蘭的Aperam SA，和蒂森克虜伯（Thyssenkrupp AG）的義大利子公司Acciai Speciali Terni SpA提出投訴後，啟動反傾銷調查。<br />\n<br />\n而EUROFER數據顯示，2018年歐盟進口的不鏽鋼板和捲材總額，接近9億歐元（約台幣316.67億）。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3127380\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3127380&d=5ySQsq589lR7QRkangxGbgNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=5238b29a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3127380&h=98bd72bd\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3127380</a><br />\n<br />\n歐盟:<a href=\"https://eur-lex.europa.eu/legal-content/EN/TXT/PDF/?uri=CELEX:32020R0508&amp;from=EN\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Feur-lex.europa.eu%2Flegal-content%2FEN%2FTXT%2FPDF%2F%3Furi%3DCELEX%3A32020R0508%26from%3DEN&d=5ySQsq589lR7QRkangxGbgNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=4fa5054c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://eur-lex.europa.eu/legal-content/EN/TXT/PDF/?uri=CELEX:32020R0508&amp;from=EN</a>"},{"pid":"50fbdd96247e74d2ac8dfa645fc58129e4a4f740","tid":1964251,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T16:29:47.000Z","msg":"台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"674f36a9e611102ea41959555d119e4ece95d097","tid":1964251,"uid":199957,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T16:42:48.000Z","msg":"佢話3國 唔認同一個中國原則呀?"},{"pid":"1f01a3c02d84e989b65f955e65c3de261735784d","tid":1964251,"uid":123738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T16:47:44.000Z","msg":"支那要反擊了，應該唔好賣比歐洲，留返黎建設支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bec80f29630e02016f9b03d89c068f9b9a0cf0ee","tid":1964251,"uid":40267,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"50fbdd96247e74d2ac8dfa645fc58129e4a4f740","tid":1964251,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T16:29:47.000Z","msg":"台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T03:05:00.000Z","msg":"都話啲垃圾歐豬白左靠唔撚著架啦<br />\n台仔捐口罩捐呼吸機結果呢<br />\n班柒頭照當台仔condom<br />\n上次歐盟講有關台仔嘅新聞咪屌佢上星期執行死刑唔人道囉<br />\n支那年年唔知幾多死刑犯政治犯隻字不提"}]}